General
-------
-BorderPane with different scenes (Center), each scene is created with a
fxml file and has it's own controller
- Invoke Initialize interface to load data in a controller from start
- Icons in Buttons
- A simple MenuBar
- FXML and images fetched from resources

Default
--------
Read this information from a file and display it in a Text area.

Screen 1
--------
-Simple event management push button, connect method, get text add it to a list
-Add code to delete from the list.
- Add Alert confirmation and validation alerts, local english language

Screen 2
--------
- A progressbar and a button to simulate a task
- binding and updating
- A Service/Task to simulate a background task running and that does not cause the
program to freeze.

Screen3
--------
 A TableView with a search TextField that has a binding to the data in the table displaying
 the filtered values



